title: El Bazar
description: A store selling artisan, organic, natural, fair trade, exports, original clothing, healing food (including vegan), creativity and more. Also a project of research and empowerment to different groups of the environment of the local forest. A percentage of profits goes to a social project in order to help people in need in the area. Some items sold are skin care, yogurt, macrame, cocoa, local coffee, pink salt and more. Online ordering available.
